Dave Ellison, portfolio manager of 
the Hennessy Large Cap Financial Fund, discusses investing in 
 Citigroup Inc. (C)  and Blackstone Group LP. Ellison talks with 
Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Taking Stock."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 07:00
 